\pard\cf1\f0\fs24\lang1033 Plan.\par
Every day make 5 - 10 sentences of the story.\par
\par
\f1\lang1049 Someone was sitting on \f0\lang1033 the\f1\lang1049  bench.\par
Someone was looking at the street.\par
\f0\lang1033 Tolya was singing.\par
Boris was silent.\par
Nikolay was wiggling his foot.\par
\par
It was in the evening.\par
They had nothing to do being bored.\par
\par
The bird sat on the fence.\par
The cat climbed into the loft.\par
And then Boris said "I have a nail in my pocket. And you?"\par
The other said "We are having a guest today. And you?".\par
The third said: "Our cat gave birth to kittens yesterday."\par
"The kittens have grown up a little, but they don't want to drink from the saucer."\par
}
